<head>
    <%- include("includes/head")%>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <%- include("includes/header", {pagename: "Add Goal"})%>
    </header>
    <main>
        <br>
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <h1>Create A Goal</h1>
            <small>Let's create a new achievable goal.</small>
        </div>
        <div style="margin: 16px;">
            <h2 style="text-align: center;">Good Goal Setting Tips</h2>
            <br>
            <h3>1. Make It Specific</h3>
            <p>Avoid vague or ambigious goals such as "get healthier" or "be smarter." Instead, be clear and focused.</p>
            <small>❌ "Exercise more."</small><br>
            <small>✅ "Go to the gym 3 times a week. Each session must be at least 30 minutes."</small>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h3>2. Make It Measureable</h3>
            <p>Track your progress. Include numbers, deadlines, or benchmarks in your goal.</p>
            <small>❌ "Read more."</small><br>
            <small>✅ "Read 1 book per month."</small>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h3>3. Make It Time Bound</h3>
            <p>Set a clear timeframe to keep yourself accountable and motivated.</p>
            <small>❌ "Write a story."</small><br>
            <small>✅ "Finish a story by July 8th."</small>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h3>4. Break it Into Steps</h3>
            <p>Large goals can be overwhelming. Break them into smaller, more achievable tasks or milestones.</p>
            <small>❌ "Launch a website."</small><br>
            <small>✅ "Learn to Code, Buy a Domain, Write Webpages, Upload Code"</small>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h3>5. Frame it Positively</h3>
            <p>Focus on what you will do, not what you're avoiding, or quitting.</p>
            <small>❌ "Stop drinking."</small><br>
            <small>✅ "Redirect evening urges to writing music every night for a month."</small>
            <br>
            <br>
            <h1 style="text-align: center;">Let's Set a Goal!</h1>
            <p>The RenewYou app allows you to set several types of goals; From long-term to single day goals, you can customize your journey however you'd like!</p>
            <br>
            <h2 style="text-align: center;">Choose Graph Type</h2>
            <p>When setting your goal, think about which graph type would fit your method of tracking the best.</p>
            <br>
            <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/progress'">
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Progress Bar</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div id="progressText" style="text-align: center;"></div>
                        <div class="progress-container">
                            <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">1-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Perfect for quantity based goals.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/line'">
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Line Graph</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <canvas id="lineChart" width="100%" height="100%"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">2-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Great way to see progress over time</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" ><!--onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/bar'"-->
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Bar Chart</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <canvas id="barChart" width="100%" height="100%"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">2-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Vertical and Horizontal Options</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Great way to compare goal progress</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" > <!--onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/pie'"-->
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Pie Chart Chart</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <canvas id="pieChart" width="100%" height="100%"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Multi-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Great for segmented goals</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/milestone'">
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Milestone</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
                            <h2>Sobriety</h2>
                            <p>95 Days</p>
                            <small>Since Aug 3rd 2024</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">1-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Great for seeing progress</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" ><!--onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/scatter'"-->
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Scatter Plot</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <canvas id="scatterChart" width="100%" height="100%"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">2-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Best for long-term goals</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/add-goal/number'">
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: center;">
                    <div>
                        <h2>Basic Number Goal</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="card" style="text-align: center;">
                            <h2>6/13</h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style="text-align: center;">1-Variable Goal</p>
                <p style="text-align: center;">Great for simple tracking</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        // Example values (can be replaced with dynamic data)
        const completed = 7;
        const total = 10;

        const percent = Math.round((completed / total) * 100);
        const bar = document.getElementById("progressBar");
        bar.style.width = percent + "%";
        document.getElementById("progressText").textContent = completed + "/" + total;

        const ctx = document.getElementById("lineChart").getContext("2d");
        const lineChart = new Chart(ctx, {
            type: "line",
            data: {
            labels: ["Jan", "Feb", "Mar", "Apr", "May", "Jun", "Jul"],
            datasets: [{
                label: "Paintings Made",
                data: [2, 3, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10],
                borderColor: "rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)",
                backgroundColor: "rgba(75, 192, 192, 0.2)",
                fill: true,
                tension: 0.3,
                pointRadius: 5,
                pointHoverRadius: 7,
            }]
            },
            options: {
            responsive: true,
            scales: {
                y: {
                beginAtZero: true,
                ticks: { stepSize: 1 }
                }
            }
            }
        });

         // Bar Chart
        const ctxBar = document.getElementById("barChart").getContext("2d");
        new Chart(ctxBar, {
            type: "bar",
            data: {
            labels: ["Mon","Tue","Wed","Thurs","Fri"],
            datasets: [{
                label: "Minutes At Gym",
                data: [45,30,0,60,20],
                backgroundColor: "rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)",
                borderColor: "rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)",
                borderWidth: 1,
                borderRadius: 4
            }]
            },
            options: {
            responsive: true,
            scales: {
                y: {
                beginAtZero: true,
                ticks: { stepSize: 1 }
                }
            }
            }
        });

        // Pie Chart
        const ctxPie = document.getElementById("pieChart").getContext("2d");
        new Chart(ctxPie, {
        type: "pie",
        data: {
            labels: ["Carbs", "Fats", "Protein"],
            datasets: [{
            data: [40, 25, 35],
            backgroundColor: [
                "rgba(255, 206, 86, 0.8)",   // carbs
                "rgba(255, 99, 132, 0.8)",   // fats
                "rgba(54, 162, 235, 0.8)"    // protein
            ],
            borderColor: "#000",
            borderWidth: 1,
            }]
        },
        options: {
            responsive: true,
            plugins: {
            legend: {
                position: "bottom"
            },
            datalabels: {
                color: "#000",
                font: {
                weight: "normal",
                size: 14
                },
                formatter: (value, ctx) => {
                const data = ctx.chart.data.datasets[0].data;
                const total = data.reduce((sum, val) => sum + val, 0);
                const percentage = ((value / total) * 100).toFixed(0);
                return percentage + "%";
                }
            }
            }
        },
        plugins: [ChartDataLabels]
        });

        const ctxScatter = document.getElementById("scatterChart").getContext("2d");

        new Chart(ctxScatter, {
        type: "scatter",
        data: {
            datasets: [{
            label: "Study Time vs Test Score",
            data: [
                { x: 1, y: 65 },
                { x: 2, y: 70 },
                { x: 3, y: 72 },
                { x: 4, y: 78 },
                { x: 5, y: 85 },
                { x: 6, y: 88 },
                { x: 7, y: 94 }
            ],
            backgroundColor: "rgba(75, 192, 192, 1)"
            }]
        },
        options: {
            responsive: true,
            plugins: {
            title: {
                display: true,
                text: "Study Time vs Test Score"
            }
            },
            scales: {
            x: {
                title: {
                display: true,
                text: "Hours Studied"
                },
                beginAtZero: true
            },
            y: {
                title: {
                display: true,
                text: "Test Score"
                },
                beginAtZero: true,
                max: 100
            }
            }
        }
        });

    });
    </script>
    <footer>
        <%- include("includes/footer", {page: 2})%>
    </footer>
</body>